<strong>Prologue: <a href="/a-confluence-of-clandestine-conferences">A Confluence of Clandestine Conferences</a></strong>
<blockquote>
<p><tt>I would very much like to investigate the Chipotle parking lot further. Please provide me with further instructions.</tt></p>
</blockquote>
<p><strong>1: <a href="/slow-animals">Slow Animals</a></strong></p>
<blockquote>
<p>He glanced over his shoulder, back at Casey. &quot;So, uh, for the record, if you are an actual murderer, it would be super uncool of you not to tell me now.&quot;</p>
</blockquote>
<p><strong>2: <a href="/automatic-stop">Automatic Stop</a></strong></p>
<blockquote>
<p>Once Vera Garcia had reported to Taco Bell and found a false bottom in her bag of one Burrito Supreme and one Crispy Chicken Quesadilla, she knew that her plan had been approved by the Rotisserie Outfitters Bureau.</p>
</blockquote>
<p><strong>3: <a href="/the-end-has-no-end">The End Has No End</a></strong></p>
<blockquote>
<p>&quot;I'm sorry, do you have friends that you have not yet murdered, amnesticized, or dragged into this death spiral with you? If so, they should <em>also</em> be leaving the city.&quot;</p>
</blockquote>
<p><strong>Intermission: <a href="/intermission">World Unglued</a></strong></p>
<blockquote>
<p><span style="color: blue">#3ports</span> <span style="color: black">What's with all the fire? Isn't unscheduled arson illegal?</span></p>
</blockquote>
<p><strong>4: <a href="/threat-of-joy">Threat of Joy</a></strong></p>
<blockquote>
<p>The light returned to Three Portlands the way it returns to a movie theatre once the credits stop rolling: sheepishly, as if embarrassed by the popcorn-strewn wasteland it had become over the course of the film.</p>
</blockquote>
<hr />
<div style="text-align: center;">
<h2 id="toc1"><span><strong>Death of an Artist</strong></span></h2>
</div>
<p><strong><a href="/what-happened-at-greenwich">The Word and The Cool Kids</a></strong></p>
<blockquote>
<p>&quot;Hey,&quot; they might say. &quot;We fought back then when the Word was something worth fighting for. We can still fight. Fight with us.&quot;</p>
</blockquote>
<p><strong><a href="/who-are-the-cool-kids">The War and The Many Faces</a></strong></p>
<blockquote>
<p>&quot;The thing you need to understand about the people who run the world, Mister Baudin, is that escape is a myth.&quot;</p>
</blockquote>
</div>
