<p><strong><a href="/a-quiet-night">A Quiet Night</a></strong> &#8212; Serpent's Hand</p>
<blockquote>
<p>Face it. The periphery is getting smaller. Soon enough, you'll either be a civilian or you'll be an employee. Make your choice.</p>
</blockquote>
